name: Mogvert
body:
### mogvert
mogvert is a fast, lightweight  and reliable  audio  reencoding  engine supporting  multiple  file  formats.  It  has a modular design allowing greater flexibility and the ability to incorperate  additional  encoder and  decoder modules with ease.

### History
* 2013-02-13 - 0.2 Release
* 2012-04-12 - Import & resurrection 
* 2004-11-08 - 0.1 (12b) snapshot 
* 2004-05-08 - Initial release
